     В                                Notes:                              л


     л  You paid your dues in THUG. Now prove yourself in THUG 2. You've 
     л  been chosen by Tony Hawk to take on Bam Margera as your teams go
     л  on a World Destruction Tour. Its time to go globetrotting on an 
     л  insane road trip. THUG 2 grinds in with a hilarious story mode, 
     л  an unprecedented level of customization, and more moves than the
     л  Skate Gods could dream of. Grab your board, an arsenal of 
     л  spray-paint... jump into the tour van and wreak havoc across the
     л  globe.
