     В                            Game Features:                          л


     л   World Destruction Tour: Hawk recruits YOU onto his team for a 
     л    no rules, no limits world tour versus Bam Margera. You invade 
     л    international cities and wreak havoc, proving yourself to the
     л    pros as you live the ultimate skateboard adventure. 
     л
     л   All New Team Play: Team Hawk versus Team Bam. Play as yourself
     л     or switch to play one of your teammates or a special guest 
     л    skater - over 20 unique characters. 
     л
     л   Unparalleled Customization: Create your own logo for use in 
     л    graffiti tags, skate stickers with the all new 
     л    'Create-A-Graphic' feature. Familiar Hawk customization 
     л    continues with 'Create-A-Goal,' 'Create-A-Park' and the 
     л    revolutionary 'Face In The Game' feature. More Player Control 
     л    Than Ever Before: Tear it up with sticker slaps, projectiles,
     л    crazy vehicles, hilarious tantrums, and slow-motion Focus
     л    Control. 
     л
     л   2 Games In 1: Team up and wreak havoc in Story Mode or switch
     л    and play 15 levels in Classic Mode. Complete your all-time 
     л    favorite goals like S-K-A-T-E, Secret Tape, and High Score 
     л    against a 2-minute timer.
